    <item>
      <title>[CON-19] Creating an article without authorization returns 401 instead of expected 403.</title>
      <link>https://darynahopanchuk-1764176161485.atlassian.net/browse/CON-19</link>
      <project id="10000" key="CON">qanov25dhopanchuk</project>
      <description>
        <p>
          <b>Test Data:</b>
        </p>
        <p>-</p>
        <p>
          <b>Steps to reproduce:</b>
        </p>
        <ol>
          <li>Send <tt>POST /articles</tt> request with the following body: <div class="code panel"
              style="border-width: 1px;">
              <div class="codeContent panelContent">
                <pre class="code-none">{ "article": { "title": "{{articleTitleConduit}}", "description": "{{articleDescriptionConduit}}", "body": "{{articleBodyConduit}}", "tagList": [] } }</pre>
              </div>
            </div></li>
          <li>Do not add Authorisation to the Headers.</li>
        </ol>
        <p>
          <b>Expected result:</b>
        </p>
        <p>The server should return 403 Forbidden with an error message indicating that article
          creation is not allowed without authentication.</p>
        <p>
          <b>Actual result:</b>
        </p>
        <p>The server returns 401 Unauthorized, signaling missing or invalid credentials.</p>
        <p>
          <a href="https://loom.com/i/73f3a45f50cf427ba25bb0de48d0d451" title="smart-card"
